            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Abnobae <lb n="2"/>sacrum <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Proclinius <lb n="4"/>Verus stator <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Z. 2: vor sacrum ein spatium von 2 Buchstaben. Autopsie R. Wiegels. Hauptbearbeiterin B. Esch.</p>
            </div>
